VALUES
(6216210, 'Now, fair spectators, a duel of monumental weight awaits us. Sir Lorenz of Theramore against the young and upcoming talent of Fritz of Kul Tiras!', 'Now, fair spectators, a duel of monumental weight awaits us. Sir Lorenz of Theramore against the young and upcoming talent of Fritz of Kul Tiras!', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216211, 'Another joust awaits! A valiant duel between Sir Barnabas of Strom, a gilded veteran of old, and the equally skilled Lumiere of Dalaran!', 'Another joust awaits! A valiant duel between Sir Barnabas of Strom, a gilded veteran of old, and the equally skilled Lumiere of Dalaran!', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216212, 'On to our next joust! To my left, a stout knight of our kingdom, Sir Reginald! To my right, from the far kingdom of Strom, Sir Rudolf!', 'On to our next joust! To my left, a stout knight of our kingdom, Sir Reginald! To my right, from the far kingdom of Strom, Sir Rudolf!', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216213, 'Silence, fair citizens, for a special bout is about to happen! Hailing under no flag and bearing no color, the Black Knight steps into the ring! His opponent: the courageous Halfar of Kul Tiras, breaker of tides and storms!', 'Silence, fair citizens, for a special bout is about to happen! Hailing under no flag and bearing no color, the Black Knight steps into the ring! His opponent: the courageous Halfar of Kul Tiras, breaker of tides and storms!', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216214, 'The next joust begins! To my left, a brave contestant from the sea-faring nation of Theramore, Sir Ferdinand! To my right, a chivalrous mage and his steadfast steed, Estanor of Dalaran!', 'The next joust begins! To my left, a brave contestant from the sea-faring nation of Theramore, Sir Ferdinand! To my right, a chivalrous mage and his steadfast steed, Estanor of Dalaran!', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216215, 'Now, let us determine which knight will bring glory to its homeland!', 'Now, let us determine which knight will bring glory to its homeland!', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216216, 'Onwards, to victory!', 'Onwards, to victory!', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216217, 'Incredible! Anyone present here at this tournament can vouch for the emotional investment brought into this duel. In the end, it is Sir Lorenz who shall be praised for this victory!', 'Incredible! Anyone present here at this tournament can vouch for the emotional investment brought into this duel. In the end, it is Sir Lorenz who shall be praised for this victory!', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216218, 'Such elegance! Lumiere effortlessly demonstrated that Dalaran should not be underestimated! A lesson Sir Barnabas felt hands-on!', 'Such elegance! Lumiere effortlessly demonstrated that Dalaran should not be underestimated! A lesson Sir Barnabas felt hands-on!', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216219, 'A clean strike! Sir Rudolf lies on the ground, defeated by the proud Sir Reginald!', 'A clean strike! Sir Rudolf lies on the ground, defeated by the proud Sir Reginald!', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216220, 'What a merciless display! Call for the doctor, I''m sure Sir Halfar sorely needs it! A gruesome reminder of how brutal these tournaments can become!', 'What a merciless display! Call for the doctor, I''m sure Sir Halfar sorely needs it! A gruesome reminder of how brutal these tournaments can become!', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216221, 'Devastating! The might of Theramore was demonstrated once more on this day! Sir Estanor could not withstand Sir Ferdinand''s mighty blow!', 'Devastating! The might of Theramore was demonstrated once more on this day! Sir Estanor could not withstand Sir Ferdinand''s mighty blow!', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216222, 'Glory to Sir Lorenz of Theramore, victor to this knightly joust!', 'Glory to Sir Lorenz of Theramore, victor to this knightly joust!', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
